Headlines.Author: Tess Stynes
Headlines.Headline: DDR, Board Agree Not to Renew CEO's Contract

PARAGRAPH.#text: DDR Corp. DDR said Chief Executive Daniel B. Hurwitz and the shopping-center owner's board agreed not to renew his contract, which expires at the end of this year. The real-estate investment trust expects Mr. Hurwitz to remain CEO through next year to help provide a smooth transition. A board committee is expected to engage an executive search firm to assist in an internal and external search for a successor for Mr. Hurwitz, who has been CEO since early 2010. Before becoming DDR's CEO, he served as chief operating officer, starting in May 2007.
